Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:41.13,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs56\move(935,1055,960,1020)}劍姬神聖譚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:41.21,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs56\move(962,1016,972,1001.6)}劍姬神聖譚
